query: CREATE TABLE default.fact_conv_5min_local UUID 'ea5387f1-731e-4e61-a093-d30b7008bbe9' (`sg_name` LowCardinality(String), `start_time_5min` DateTime, `end_time_5min` DateTime, `int_ipv4` IPv4, `app_key` LowCardinality(String), `line` LowCardinality(String), `pipe` LowCardinality(String), `vc` LowCardinality(String), `tether_indication` LowCardinality(String), `next_hop_as` UInt64, `destination_as` UInt64, `app_group_key` LowCardinality(String), `subscriber_key` String, `live_connections` UInt64, `volume_in` UInt64, `volume_out` UInt64, `degrade_volume_in` UInt64, `degrade_volume_out` UInt64, `drop_connections` UInt64, `bandwidth_in` Float64 DEFAULT toUInt64((volume_in * 8) / 300), `bandwidth_out` Float64 DEFAULT toUInt64((volume_out * 8) / 300)) ENGINE = MergeTree PARTITION BY toStartOfHour(start_time_5min) ORDER BY (start_time_5min, app_key) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192
